## WHAT IS MISSING — THIS IS YOUR BUILD TARGET

The scenes load but contain no real world. They are mostly flat planes with Label3D nodes and spawned cubes. The player can technically move but there is nothing to see, nothing to interact with, and nothing that feels like a game. Build the following, in order, one scene at a time, verifying each before moving on.

